Program: Outlook
Title: Body Parts for Sale in China
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrx4
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
New rules for organ transplants in China regarding having written permission before the sale of organs from executed criminals. Quilombos in Brazil, the descendents of slaves winning official ownership of their land. Global warming bringing famine in DRC. The car mechanic in Senegal who adopted 50 children. Norah Vincent's story of living as a man for 18 months. Show less